## 8. Pre-Push & PRA Quick Reference

### Pre-push hook (runs automatically before `git push`):
1. `./gradlew detekt` — static analysis
2. `./gradlew apiCheck` — binary compatibility
3. `./gradlew sortDependencies` — dependency ordering
4. `./gradlew spotlessApply` — auto-format code

### PRA CI (runs on every pull request):
1. `spotlessCheck` — verify formatting
2. `checkSortDependencies` — verify dependency order
3. `apiCheck` — binary compatibility
4. `detekt` — static analysis
5. `lint` — Android lint
6. `test` — unit tests
7. `assemble` — build verification
8. `buildHealth` — dependency hygiene

### Local verification:
```bash
# Run all pre-push checks manually
./pre-validation.sh

# Or run individually
./gradlew detekt
./gradlew spotlessCheck
./gradlew apiCheck
./gradlew checkSortDependencies
./gradlew lint
./gradlew buildHealth
```
